Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:32.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:34.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Canvas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.95,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:37.29,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll be in the next episode, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.29,0:24:38.36,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With the Detective Boys again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.36,0:24:39.72,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Should we dive back in?
